# Adding new migrations

* Create new directory in `migrations/` with the version to migrate to
* Add script migrate.py with all changes to metadata.xml
* Change version in localTesting.sh and irodsUpdater.sh to new version

# Local testing of migrations

* Create new directory in testing with version to migrate to
* Add *.xml files tot test on to this directory
* Run `./diff.sh -p | colordiff` to review changes

# Dry run of migrations on iRODs

* Get a working rodsadmin connection through iinit to iRODS server of choice
* Run `./irodsUpdater.sh` to execute updater
* Run `./diff.sh -p | colordiff` to review changes

# Commit changes

* Get a working rodsadmin connection through iinit to iRODS server of choice
* Run `./irodsUpdater.sh --commit` to execute updater in commit mode
* Run `./diff.sh -p | colordiff` to review changes

